Barro, Galbraith Debate Stimulus Vs. Austerity for U.S.

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-15T23:23:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/barro-galbraith-debate-stimulus-vs-austerity-for-u-s-video.html
Robert Barro, an economics 
professor at  Harvard University , and James Galbraith, a 
professor at the  University of Texas  in Austin, talk about the 
 U.S. economy , the effectiveness of fiscal austerity versus 
stimulus and ways to spur growth.  They speak with  Matt Miller  and Lisa Murphy on Bloomberg 
Television's "Street Smart." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:57
 